tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedbackSentiments (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id UUID,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  sentiment_score FLOAT,
  analyzed_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE feedback_sentiments (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    sentiment_score DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE customer_profiles (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(50),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE trend_analysis_results (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_date DATE,
    trend_label VARCHAR(50),
    trend_score DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE report_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    report_id INT,
    report_date DATE,
    report_text TEXT
)
